metadata.name: GQ3 #1
metadata.description: Join us in GQ's exciting new venture into web3 with the release of our digital collection, GQ3 Issue 001: Change Is Good!  To celebrate GQ3 Issue 001: Change Is Good being just one week away, we will be raffling off 300 FCFS  spots to our General Allowlist! Winners will be notified by email and will be included in the second phase of our mint. For an FAQ and more information on our allowlist, visit our discord.
